### ============================================
### 팀 편성 API
### ============================================

### 6. 랜덤 팀 배정 (2팀)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/random
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "932L",
  "teamCount": 2
}

### 7. 팀 초기화
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "932L"
}

### 8. 사다리타기 (2팀) - 애니메이션 데이터 포함
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/ladder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "932L",
  "teamCount": 2
}

### 9. 수동 팀 선택 (플레이어가 직접)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/select
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "여기에_roomId",
  "deviceId": "플레이어_deviceId",
  "teamName": "A"
}

### 10. 현재 팀 상태 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/teams/status/여기에_roomId

